Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000002583FC292D0> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Shortest duration of a single 'Unmatched + Unmatched' activity
